The title of '''House leader''' was borne by the premiers on at least some of the twenty-eight colony worlds of the [[Chiss Ascendancy/Legends|Chiss Ascendancy]]. The House leaders were responsible for appointing the [[Syndic/Legends|Syndics]] of their worlds' [[Phalanx (Chiss)|Colonial Phalanxes]], and they also represented their planets in the [[Chiss/Legends|Chiss]] [[Chiss Senate|Parliament]], which met in the [[House Palace]] in [[Csaplar/Legends|Csaplar]], on the Ascendancy's capital world of [[Csilla/Legends|Csilla]]. The title of House leader was included in a study produced by the [[University of Sanbra]] in the last years of the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]].

